{"tid":1560814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］［警世］切勿將911事件當成閒聊話題","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T12:59:33.000Z","uid":263913,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a74df0a3617209662f320e6abbcc449dde085f30","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"見倒頭先有個巴打開咗post講911發生嘅時候大家做緊咩<br />\n相信開post嘅人同大部分覆post嘅都無惡意的<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">911事件死咗好多無辜嘅平民<br />\n而源起就正正係因為恐怖主義行為</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地諗下過咗好多年後<br />\n有人講起香港烈士犧牲嘅時候，大家當時做緊咩，會有咩感受？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n覆咗post嘅就算啦<br />\n小妹我都一開始唔為意覆咗post<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家開始唔好再出呢種post、再覆呢種post好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">We are sorry to cause any disrespect in the 911 tragedy.<br />\nWe sincerely apologise for any of that.<br />\nPlease forgive our stupidity.<br />\nHong Kong people do stand with US and we do grieve the victim in 911 tragedy.</span>"},{"pid":"8e1e2e5b110ae7c3b4324b4d695176dee971e892","tid":1560814,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"408d84361acb31ce6f81e187b29292ba47fd7273","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"e12605659f6d724f4ca3e6b4a635cd5092e3be7a","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"d73f79914b87b2c5ce86e7ca7bfc140aebaf31c9","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"1dfe6ea0a3ccccc74784fd2b90570580371ad70c","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"b22d67e0ba32d40e6772f8f595802da5b4c7428a","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"c1d5ca1e5a68cb7d80d20a293f496f441a61fd2d","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"f9e23dc72766ef60a9990f1c391ecdd1a8137264","tid":1560814,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:06:49.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺 <br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"2428c896024fd4d449abccd305c71081e5e30502","tid":1560814,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"討論下姐 好似我地討論納粹 日軍咁<br />\n最緊要唔講笑咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20d2cc03da3c9272f85ef583c4306f03d1adc03","tid":1560814,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"痴線 歷史事件拎嚟討論返有咩問題"},{"pid":"54cc6eafd0cbf91c8514f2c